#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch03-02-data-types.md:449
msgid ""
"The main way to use Boolean values is through conditionals, such as an `if`\n"
"expression. We’ll cover how `if` expressions work in Rust in the [“Control\n"
