msgid ""
"```rust\n"
"{{#rustdoc_include ../listings-sources/ch06-enums-and-pattern-matching/"
"listing-06-02/src/main.rs:here}}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```rust\n"
"{{#rustdoc_include ../listings/ch06-enums-and-pattern-matching/listing-06-02/"
"src/main.rs:here}}\n"
"```"

#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch06-01-defining-an-enum.md:355
msgid ""
"<span class=\"caption\">Listing 6-2: A `Message` enum whose variants each "
"store\n"
"different amounts and types of values</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"caption\">Encart 6-2 : Une énumération `Message` dont chaque\n"
"variante stocke des valeurs de différents types et en différentes\n"
"quantités</span>"

