"```rust,ignore\n"
"{{#rustdoc_include ../listings/ch07-managing-growing-projects/listing-07-21-"
"and-22/src/lib.rs}}\n"
"```"

#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch07-05-separating-modules-into-different-files.md:49
