#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch10-02-traits.md:384
msgid ""
"Creating a default implementation for `summarize` doesn’t require us to "
"change\n"
"anything about the implementation of `Summary` on `Tweet` in Listing 10-13. "
"The\n"
"reason is that the syntax for overriding a default implementation is the "
"same\n"
"as the syntax for implementing a trait method that doesn’t have a default\n"
"implementation."
msgstr ""
