#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch11-01-writing-tests.md:796
msgid ""
"Our test caught the bug! The `it_adds_two` test failed, displaying the "
"message\n"
"`` assertion failed: `(left == right)` `` and showing that `left` was `4` "
