#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch11-01-writing-tests.md:990
msgid ""
"This result just indicates that the assertion failed and which line the\n"
"assertion is on. A more useful failure message in this case would print the\n"
"value we got from the `greeting` function. Let’s change the test function,\n"
"giving it a custom failure message made from a format string with a "
