"```"
msgstr ""
"```rust,ignore\n"
"{{#rustdoc_include ../listings/ch11-writing-automated-tests/no-listing-07-"
"custom-failure-message/src/lib.rs:here}}\n"
"```"

#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch11-01-writing-tests.md:1015
msgid "Now when we run the test, we’ll get a more informative error message:"
msgstr ""

#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch11-01-writing-tests.md:1022
msgid ""
"```console\n"
"{{#include ../listings/ch11-writing-automated-tests/no-listing-07-custom-"
"failure-message/output.txt}}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```console\n"
"{{#include ../listings/ch11-writing-automated-tests/no-listing-07-custom-"
"failure-message/output.txt}}\n"
