"A type alias makes this code more manageable by reducing the repetition. In\n"
"Listing 19-25, we’ve introduced an alias named `Thunk` for the verbose type "
"and\n"
"can replace all uses of the type with the shorter alias `Thunk`."
msgstr ""
"Un alias de type simplifie ce code en réduisant la répétition. Dans "
"l'encart\n"
"19-25, nous avons ajouté un alias `Thunk` pour ce type verbeux, alias plus\n"
