msgid ""
"The `Result<..., Error>` is repeated a lot. As such, `std::io` has this "
"type\n"
"alias declaration:"
msgstr ""
"Le `Result<..., Error>` est répété plein de fois. C'est pourquoi `std::io`\n"
"possède cette déclaration d'alias de type :"

#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch19-04-advanced-types.md:278
msgid ""
"```rust,noplayground\n"
"{{#rustdoc_include ../listings-sources/ch19-advanced-features/no-listing-06-"
