#: /home/pierre/dev/rust-book-fr/FRENCH/src/ch20-01-single-threaded.md:982
msgid ""
"Here, our response has a status line with status code 404 and the reason\n"
"phrase `NOT FOUND`. The body of the response will be the HTML in the file\n"
"*404.html*. You’ll need to create a *404.html* file next to *hello.html* "
"for\n"
"the error page; again feel free to use any HTML you want or use the example\n"
"HTML in Listing 20-8."
msgstr ""
